        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer15663503&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer15663503" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14694986688945439274">I loved the tension between romance and desparation. The author held a fine line between these two emotions -- something often missing in his Thomas Covenant Chronicles.</span>

          </span>
